<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
      <h2><%= get('github_login') %></h2>
        <hr class="star-primary">
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row nav-buttons">
    <div class="btn-group btn-group-justified">
      <div class="general btn-group settings">
        <button type="button" class="active btn btn-default">Settings</button>
      </div>
      <div class="active rules btn-group recentStats">
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-default">Recent Stats</button>
      </div>
      <div class="btn-group lifetimeStats">
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-default">Lifetime Stats</button>
      </div>
      <div class="btn-group averageStats">
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-default">Average Stats</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row info-list">
    <p class="col-lg-8 col-lg-offset-2">
      You are currently signed up for the next JavaScript Battle.  We will pull your code from the GitHub repository listed below. Feel free to update this repository at any time (we will pull your most up-to-date code from your GitHub account before each battle).
    </p>
  </div>
  <p class="col-lg-8 col-lg-offset-2">
    Note #1: If you have not already forked our <a target="_blank" href="https://github.com/JSJitsu/ai-battle-website">hero-starter</a> repository, go to <a target="_blank" href="https://github.com/JSJitsu/ai-battle-website">this link</a> and click "Fork" in the top right.  If you don't do this, we won't be able to find your hero code, so your hero will not have a brain (and will just "stand there" for the entire battle)!
  </p>
  <p class="col-lg-8 col-lg-offset-2">
    Note #2: If you signed up recently and want to customize/improve your hero code (your hero's "brain"),
    <a target="_blank" href="https://github.com/JSJitsu/ai-battle-website">check out our hero-starter README.</a> (After clicking the link, scroll down to see the instructions).
  </p>
  <div class="row">
    <form class="form-inline repoInput text-center" role="form">
      <div class="form-group">
        <label class="control-label" for="inputRepo">GitHub Repository</label>
        <input type="text" class="form-control" id="inputRepo" value="<%= get('code_repo') %>">
        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-ok form-control-feedback"></span>
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-default submitRepo">Save</button>
      </div>
    </form>
  </div>
  <div class="text-center">
    <a href="/logout" type="button" class="btn btn-default logoutButton">
      <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-log-out">&nbsp;</i>Log out
    </a>
  </div>
</div>